#21000
Soot-Choked Entry Vault~
Soot-Choked Entry Vault narrows into a solemn pocket of the Nightfall Catacombs. A sour incense settles behind your eyes; the chamber is marked by sarcophagus lids carved with penitent kings. A low organ-note hums through the mortar and into your bones. Finger marks mar the dust at shoulder height all around.~
