Reliquary Entry Vault~
Reliquary Entry Vault narrows into a solemn pocket of the Nightfall Catacombs. The scent of old marrow lingers here; the chamber is marked by frescoes of eclipsed suns peeled by moisture. A low organ-note hums through the mortar and into your bones. Several stones are warm to the touch despite the cold.~
