Hollow Torches' Reach~
Hollow Torches' Reach narrows into a solemn pocket of the Nightfall Catacombs. The air tastes of wet limestone and ash; the chamber is marked by bas-reliefs of mourners with empty faces. A low organ-note hums through the mortar and into your bones. Dried blood maps a path that vanishes at the far wall.~
