#21071
Candle-Dripped Torches' Reach~
Candle-Dripped Torches' Reach narrows into a solemn pocket of the Nightfall Catacombs. The smell of rusted iron dominates this chamber; the chamber is marked by charnel gutters etched into the floorstones. From the next turn comes the drag of chain over slate. Fresh scratch marks score the threshold in parallel lines.~
