#21072
Bone-Lit Silent Crossing~
Bone-Lit Silent Crossing narrows into a solemn pocket of the Nightfall Catacombs. Your breath mists in thin silver ribbons; the chamber is marked by alcoves packed with jawless skulls. Distant boots march in cadence, then stop the moment you listen. A black feather drifts in a draft that should not exist.~
