#21073
Blackwater Silent Crossing~
Blackwater Silent Crossing narrows into a solemn pocket of the Nightfall Catacombs. The scent of old marrow lingers here; the chamber is marked by shattered reliquaries spilling saint-bone splinters. You hear brittle clicking, as if teeth chatter inside the walls. A toppled idol has been turned to face the entrance.~
