#21074
Gloambound Winding Aisle~
Gloambound Winding Aisle narrows into a solemn pocket of the Nightfall Catacombs. Tallow smoke clings to your tongue; the chamber is marked by chains looped through cracked memorial pillars. Muted chanting rises, then collapses into absolute silence. A cracked mirror tile reflects only darkness behind you.~
